About

Welcome to Matt O’Leary Design!

I’m a seasoned designer with a passion for creating visually compelling and effective marketing solutions. My experience spans marketing agencies, in-house design for a large retailer, and working with startups, where I’ve developed impactful branding and graphic design for digital and print media. I specialize in optimizing websites and marketing materials for conversion, using strategic design, SEO principles, and lead generation tactics to drive engagement. By blending creativity with data-driven marketing strategies, I help businesses enhance their brand and connect with their customers.

What I Offer

I specialize in providing bespoke design services tailored to meet your unique needs. Whether you're a startup looking to establish a brand identity, a small business in need of a website makeover, or an organization aiming to enhance your visual communications, I am here to help. I’m adept at combining my creativity with technical and practical know-how to bring your vision to life.

  • Branding & Identity: Crafting memorable and impactful brands from the ground up.
  • Graphic Design: Creating eye-catching designs for print and digital media.
  • Web Design: Building responsive, user-friendly websites that drive engagement and sales (eCommerce).
  • UX/UI Design: Designing intuitive interfaces that enhance user experience.

See all services

Why Choose Me?

With 15+ years of design experience across marketing agencies, mid-sized businesses, and startups, I bring a well-rounded perspective to every project. Choosing Matt O’Leary Design means working directly with me on every aspect of your project. This personalized approach ensures clear communication, attention to detail, and a deep understanding of your vision and goals. Additionally, I follow a mini-agency model where if I can leverage my contacts to expand creative jobs as needed.
